 The
Minister of the FCT, Malam Muhammad Musa Bello has offered the heartfelt
condolences of the FCT Administration and the residents of the FCT to President
Muhammadu Buhari and the entire Abba Kyari family on the passing of Malam Abba
Kyari, Chief of Staff to the President. The
Minister described the late Chief of Staff as a quintessential administrator
whose great wealth of experience spanning both the public and private sectors
was positively brought to bear in the management of the affairs of the country
including the FCT. He
prayed that Almighty Allah (SWT) grants him eternal rest in Jannatul Firdaus
and gives his family the strength to bear the loss.